*** Begin Patch
*** Add File: docs/superpowers/plans/2026-05-15-agent-workbench-mvp.md
+# Agent Workbench MVP Implementation Plan
+
+> **For agentic workers:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:subagent-driven-development (recommended) or superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task. Steps use checkbox (`- [ ]`) syntax for tracking.
+
+**Goal:** Build the first usable local web MVP of the AI software project manager workbench from the approved UI/UX design.
+
+**Architecture:** Start with a Vite + React + TypeScript single-page app backed by typed in-memory fixtures. Keep the first version local-only: the UI owns navigation, workflow state, manual gates, settings, and logs; real runner process control is represented through interfaces and fixtures so it can be connected later without rewriting the screens.
+
+**Tech Stack:** Vite, React, TypeScript, CSS modules or plain scoped CSS, Vitest, Testing Library, Playwright browser verification.
+
+---
+
+## Current Inputs
+
+- Design spec: `docs/superpowers/specs/2026-05-15-agent-workbench-ui-design.md`
+- Review page: `mockups/agent-workbench-review-page.html`
+- High-fidelity mockup: `mockups/agent-workbench-ui.html`
+- Static preview: `mockups/agent-workbench-ui-preview.svg`
+
+## File Structure
+
+- Create: `package.json` for scripts and dependencies.
+- Create: `index.html` as the Vite mount point.
+- Create: `src/main.tsx` to mount React.
+- Create: `src/App.tsx` to compose the shell, workspace, settings, and logs.
+- Create: `src/domain/workbench.ts` for typed project, task, agent, workflow, gate, memory, and capability models.
+- Create: `src/data/fixtures.ts` for the first local dataset copied from the design.
+- Create: `src/components/AppShell.tsx` for sidebar, topbar, global search, and route tabs.
+- Create: `src/components/WorkspaceDashboard.tsx` for metrics, task tree, current run, manual gate, and engineering feedback.
+- Create: `src/components/SettingsCenter.tsx` for User settings, Role Library, Workflow Library, Project Workflow, Memory, and Capability Packs.
+- Create: `src/components/RunnerLogs.tsx` for project/task/run filtered log output.
+- Create: `src/styles.css` for the dark dense workbench design system.
+- Create: `src/__tests__/workbench-model.test.ts` for data-model coverage.
+- Create: `src/__tests__/manual-gate.test.tsx` for gate interaction coverage.
+- Create: `src/__tests__/settings-center.test.tsx` for settings navigation and workflow display coverage.
+
+---
+
+### Task 1: Project Scaffold
+
+**Files:**
+- Create: `package.json`
+- Create: `index.html`
+- Create: `src/main.tsx`
+- Create: `src/App.tsx`
+- Create: `src/styles.css`
